Package: linbo-docker
Architecture: all
Depends: docker-ce | docker.io, docker-compose-plugin, jq, curl, openssl, cron
Recommends: git
Description: LINBO Docker — Modern Caching Server for linuxmuster.net 7.3
 Dockerized LINBO network boot solution that replaces the traditional
 linuxmuster-cachingserver-satellite package. Provides PXE boot, DHCP,
 image sync, remote management, and a modern web interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Auto-discovery from LMN server (zero manual config)
  - Full ISC DHCP server for school networks
  - GRUB/start.conf sync via Authority API
  - Image pull/push with resume support
  - SSH remote commands to LINBO clients
  - React web dashboard with real-time monitoring
  - Swagger API documentation
